  "text": "In order to facilitate such design, the abstraction and aggregation methods would have to generate all the necessary combinations of transformed datasets. All the corresponding DTs and the associated statistic results must be computed and stored up prior to the visualization. Readers who are interested in the technical details are referred to [CITATION_1] .",
